The paper deals with the problem of optimal request routing and content caching in a network, which is a topic related to network optimization and performance. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses the complexity of the problem and proposes algorithms to find approximate solutions, which are topics related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also mentions the use of simulations to evaluate the performance of the proposed algorithms, which is a topic related to social and information networks (cs.SI) and information theory (cs.IT).
